---
title: Butterflied Chicken with Leek & Feta Topping and Minted Potatoes
description: For tonight’s dinner, we’ve sourced potatoes from our awesome potato people at Linroyale. They have been selecting their little bundles of treasure for four generations now and put an incredible amount of passion and care into what they do. Go
check them out at www.linroyale.co.uk to see where your ’taters come from!
